space.devport.utils.item

Interface ItemPrefab

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Cloneable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ItemPrefabImpl

    public interface ItemPrefab
extends Cloneable
    ItemPrefab is used to effectively build, edit and check items.
